# CODEOWNERS — review routing for Meetropolis
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern>  <owner-1> [owner-2 ...]
#   Owners are GitHub usernames or @org/team slugs.
#   Patterns later in the file take precedence on conflict.
#
# Initial fallback: every change is reviewed by the maintainers team
# (@lass-machen/maintainers). Add or remove reviewers by managing that team
# on GitHub; membership is documented in GOVERNANCE.md.

# Default owner for everything
*                                       @lass-machen/maintainers

# Server-side (AGPL-3.0-only)
