/apps/npc-service/                      @lass-machen/maintainers
/apps/loadtest/                         @lass-machen/maintainers

# Web client (MIT) — touches game engine + AV pipeline
/apps/web/                              @lass-machen/maintainers

# Shared types (MIT) — breaking changes here affect both editions
